!.env.example

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docs (not needed in image)
*.md
!README.md
LICENSE
VINSTUB-*.docx
~$*.docx

# Test & coverage
coverage
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
vitest.config.*
